ДЗ Сентимент-анализ предложений с помощью линейных моделей¶

$$ Q = \frac{1}{l} \sum_{i = 1}^{l} log(1 + e^{-y_i(X_i, w)}) + \frac{1}{2}||w||^2 \dashrightarrow min $$

: $$ \nabla Q = \frac{1}{l} \sum_{i = 1}^{l} \frac{-y_iX_i}{1 + e^{y_i(X_i, w)}} + w $$

X - $l$ $n$, y - X, w - $n$.

def preprocessing(string):
    string = string.lower()
    string = re.sub('[^\w\s]', ' ', string)
    string = ' '.join(string.split('\n'))
    return string

In [70]:
df_train = pd.read_csv('toxic_train.csv')
y = np.array(df_train['is_toxic'], dtype=int)
y = 2 * y - 1
corpus_train = list(df_train['comment_text'].map(preprocessing))
df_test = pd.read_csv('toxic_test.csv')
y_test = np.array(df_test['is_toxic'], dtype=int)
y_test = y_test * 2 - 1
corpus_test = list(df_test['comment_text'].map(preprocessing))
In [71]:
K = [1, 2, 3, 10, 20]
In [72]:
to_drow = {}
for k in K:
    vectorizer = CountVectorizer(min_df=k)
    X = vectorizer.fit_transform(corpus_train)
    X_test = vectorizer.transform(corpus_test)
    X = sp.sparse.hstack((X, np.ones(X.shape[0])[:, None]))
    X_test = sp.sparse.hstack((X_test, np.ones(X_test.shape[0])[:, None]))
    X = X.tocsr()
    X_test = X_test.tocsr()
    w_0 = np.zeros(X.shape[1])
    sgd = SGDClassifier('binary_logistic',
                    batch_size=10000,
                    step_alpha=0.1,
                    step_beta=0,
                    l2_coef=1e-6)
    history = sgd.fit(X,
                  y,
                  w_0,
                  True,
                  X_test=X_test,
                  y_test=y_test)
    to_drow[f'{k}'] = history

plt.xlabel('', fontsize=14)          
plt.ylabel('Accuracy', fontsize=14)
plt.title('Accuracy   ', fontsize=22)

to_drow = {}
for k in K:
    vectorizer = CountVectorizer(min_df=9,max_df=k)
    X = vectorizer.fit_transform(corpus_train)
    X_test = vectorizer.transform(corpus_test)
    X = sp.sparse.hstack((X, np.ones(X.shape[0])[:, None]))
    X_test = sp.sparse.hstack((X_test, np.ones(X_test.shape[0])[:, None]))
    X = X.tocsr()
    X_test = X_test.tocsr()
    w_0 = np.zeros(X.shape[1])
    sgd = SGDClassifier('binary_logistic',
                    batch_size=10000,
                    step_alpha=0.1,
                    step_beta=0,
                    l2_coef=1e-6)
    history = sgd.fit(X,
                  y,
                  w_0,
                  True,
                  X_test=X_test,
                  y_test=y_test)
    to_drow[f'{k}'] = history
